  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Series-produced helium II cryostats for the LHC magnets: Technical choices, industrialisation, costs</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="269" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
